<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>450</hymn_number>
<author>Chawngkhupa</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw lungsiettu Pathien in,
 I lunggil sung ahin;
 Thagau ei piek kipahna,
 Khawvel chitna'n a phazo puoi.

[V2]
 Miching, mihiem hinna hin,
 Hun gel dawk zo hiel puo'n au ie!
 Ka Hukdampa Na thuguk hi.

[V3]
 2. A thukin a sang na e!
 Khawvel chitna sangin;
 Pathien hehpihna thu hi,
 Van leh khawvel ah a dim hi.

[V4]
 3. Aw, kei gilo mangthaisa,
 A lungsietna vangin;
 Thagau ei piek Hinna hi,
 Aw, ka hinna Lalpa pak in.</lyrics>
<title>THE GOD OF LOVE</title>
</song>